    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Bibleverses</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-weight:normal;">In this textfield you enter all bibleverses that you need:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Bibleverses.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="50.00%" width="322" height="182" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The way to enter the verses are usually a verse or couple of verses per line.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">Examples</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
